Got to play the WSSL stage at Spartanburg&rsquo;s Spring Fling this year with The Social Contracts. If you haven&rsquo;t heard TSC yet, make sure to check out the self-titled album from this past year. The city of Spartanburg was, of course, a gracious host and really knows how to put on a polished street fair.
